### Ticket API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Get All Tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticket/tickets/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Create New Ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticket/tickets/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "subject": "Problem with gym equipment",
    "status": "open"
}

### 3. Get Ticket Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticket/tickets/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update Ticket
PUT {{baseUrl}}/ticket/tickets/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "subject": "Updated ticket subject",
    "status": "pending",
    "admin": 2
}

### 5. Partial Update Ticket
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/ticket/tickets/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "resolved"
}

### 6. Delete Ticket
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/ticket/tickets/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get All Ticket Messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticket/ticket-messages/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Create New Ticket Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticket/ticket-messages/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ticket": 1,
    "message": "I need help with the treadmill on the second floor"
}

### 9. Get Ticket Message Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticket/ticket-messages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Update Ticket Message
PUT {{baseUrl}}/ticket/ticket-messages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ticket": 1,
    "message": "Updated message content"
}

### 11. Delete Ticket Message
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/ticket/ticket-messages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Get Messages for Specific Ticket
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticket/ticket-messages/?ticket=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Get User's Tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticket/tickets/?creator=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Get Assigned Tickets (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticket/tickets/?admin=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. Filter Tickets by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticket/tickets/?status=open
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
